        "cooked": "<p>When looking at this post:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"66930\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/3ec8ea/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/forwarding-a-text-image-video-message-why-is-it-showing-as-two-separate-messages/66930\">Forwarding a text+image/video message — why is it showing as two separate messages?</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/ux/ios-ux-ui/29\"><span data-category-id=\"29\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #B01C2A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #FF4242;\" data-parent-category-id=\"28\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square --has-parent\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">iOS UI/UX</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    See the attached image — why is the combined message showing up as two separate messages to be forwarded? \n <a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/3/1/31b4bdf8628cc97765be5b1de09088d484911752.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/31b4bdf8628cc97765be5b1de09088d484911752\" title=\"Image\">[Image]</a>\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<p>I realized that the android selection UI is quite different. When the last message in a chat is an image with text and this message is selected, the text isn’t readable and the “unselect” button for the text, mentioned in the post above, can not be tapped because it is obscured.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/9/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae\" title=\"1000019008\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae_2_214x500.png\" alt=\"1000019008\" data-base62-sha1=\"zBEIhGBHaJLYCUztbp2mSH7qffg\" width=\"214\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae_2_214x500.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae_2_321x750.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/9/f98dcf1325ca68fa11d9dad043e036ec008497ae_2_428x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"5F6061\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">1000019008</span><span class=\"informations\">898×2098 198 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>It is possible to scroll down and see/select the text, but it seems a bit ugly from a UI perspective:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/4/d/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2\" title=\"1000019011\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/d/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2_2_214x500.png\" alt=\"1000019011\" data-base62-sha1=\"b31ErPmzecX2Y9i1dZMHfMgbcQy\" width=\"214\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/d/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2_2_214x500.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/d/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2_2_321x750.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/d/4d6f7ff18f24eea807a0f77da8c1d61f33ff0cd2_2_428x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"57605C\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">1000019011</span><span class=\"informations\">898×2098 208 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>What are your thoughts on this?</p>",
